Demirel's two-day visit would focus on enhancing the bilateral
ties and the latest developments of the regional situation,
including the Kosovo issue.
</P>
<P>
"Turkey continues to actively participate in all efforts to
preserve peace and stability in the region and, in this
framework, gives great value to taking the views of Albania and
other regional countries into account," the statement added.
