anyone for the purpose of paying courtesy calls on Mr Gadhafi,"
she said at a news conference before a meeting with Egyptian
Foreign Minister Amr Moussa.
</P>
<P>
Moussa said that Mubarak's call on Gadhafi "lies within the
parameters of Arab traditions and neighborly relations."  
