<HEADLINE> Indonesia's Textile Exports Jump in 1st Quarter </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
JAKARTA, July 11 (Xinhua) -- Indonesia's exports of textile and
textile-related products jumped 50.8 percent in the first three
months of this year, according to media reports Saturday.
</P>
<P>
