<HEADLINE> Costa Rican President Deplores Algerian Veto </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SAN JOSE, July 10 (Xinhua) -- Costa Rican President Miguel
Angel Rodriguez on Friday deplored the decision by the Algerian
government to veto the presence of Costa Rican Deputy Sonia
