</P>
<P>
-- Admiral Joseph Prueher, commander-in-chief of the United
States Pacific Command, on Friday expressed optimism about the
Philippine Senate's ratification on the proposed Visiting Forces
Agreement during the Philippines-U.S. Mutual Defense Board Meeting
held here.
</P>
<P>
Malaya:
</P>
<P>
